This was pretty good. I simplified it by cooking 1 cup rice with 2 c. chicken broth and 1/2 tsp turmeric in the rice cooker, and it came out perfectly. It had a subtle flavor from the turmeric and a gorgeous yellow color. It went well with the chicken. I'd make it again.

