Rating: 4
This is so easy and the taste is amazing. It has a wonderfully buttery taste even though there is no butter in the recipe. However, I tried to double the recipe for a party and it lost something in translation. Carefully watch the rice around the 15 minute mark; 18 minutes seemed a bit too long. Don't skip the turmeric; it is essential to the color.